description: The Torin AT10152B steel scissor lift jack car kit is a collapsible, compact jack can be used as a rugged replacement jack or as an extra utility jack that can be stored in the trunk of your car. Engineered using a drop forged alloyed steel construction for quality and durability and features a lifting range of 4-1/8" to 15-1/8" with a 1.5 ton (3,000 lb) capacity. It's equipped with an extra-wide base which adds stability and strength. The 1 piece handle delivers on-the-spot quick response and speed to get the job done quickly and safely. This unit is 100% factory tested for reliability and safety to meet and comply with ANSI/ASME PASE safety standards. Includes a limited 1 year manufacturer warranty.
